      "writtenOn": "2019-12-16T22:19:56Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Continuing my comment about naming this class StreamPipeline:\n\nHow are you planning on setting up the pipeline to log the minidump?\n\nDo we need to re-implement this read-buffer-write loop for each pipeline we set up or can it be re-used for any pipeline?",
